{"tid":2059974,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲女職業賽車手逆境求生， 轉行改拍成人片！","createTime":"2020-06-11T09:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T12:42:53.000Z","uid":70105,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"79ba022a501830f9cb1b87e0ad33c8ff4d9a2057","tid":2059974,"uid":70105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T09:59:54.000Z","msg":"澳洲史上首位參賽 V8 Supercars 之 女車手 Renee Gracie ，突然宣佈決定退出賽車運動，轉而加入成人電影界，震驚當地賽車壇 ！<br />\n<br />\n現年25歲的 Renee 接受每日電訊報 (Daily Telegraph) 訪問中透露，她決定下海出演成人色情作品賺錢，表示這是她迄今為止做出的 最佳決定， 並且此行動得到家人鼎力支持<br />\n<br />\nRenee 雖然貴為賽車手， 並曾經出賽 V8 Supercars， 賽車生涯表面風光，但隨著賽車比賽成績未如理想，也沒有得到贊助資金。曾經 零收入 渡日， 又一度於汽車維修廠擔任技工， 最終賽車手夢醒， 決定到此為止<br />\n<br />\n對於轉投成人電影界 : &ldquo;這是我一生中所做的最好的事情。這使我處於從未有過的夢想中，我真的很喜歡。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo; 無論外界任何批判, 都無怨無悔。因為我賺了很多錢，對自己現況很滿意 &quot;<br />\n<br />\n自從 Renee 接受訪問以來，其網站訂閱人數激增 5000多人，該網站於上周公開。<br />\n現在，她通過在成人訂閱網站 <a href=\"http://onlyfans.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fonlyfans.com&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjREzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=7df27cc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">onlyfans.com</a> 上出售自己的視頻和圖片，每月收入超過 90000 美元<br />\n<br />\nRenee 表示 : &quot; 在頭六天內，我賺了24000 美元，那時我意識到此行業大有可為 &rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nV8 Supercars 賽會 同時發表了一份聲明，說他們知道 Renne之舉動以及隨後的採訪，清楚地表明賽會 與 該前賽車手無關 (即係割蓆)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/220513868005310/posts/3146326522090682/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F220513868005310%2Fposts%2F3146326522090682%2F&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjREzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=2dd108f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/220513868005310/posts/3146326522090682/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JF3ZcHQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJF3ZcHQ.jpg&h=e4e85ba4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d8b3a3a5f15c33cb4feedae2cfb2b58ccd752ab","tid":2059974,"uid":273157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T10:01:03.000Z","msg":"佢岩岩撞完車？個氣墊肉色既"},{"pid":"65da4fd057dc8a544634296d1bdf5b916295d8d0","tid":2059974,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T10:01:27.000Z","msg":"Renee：身體自主"},{"pid":"46f7a4d7ccb86ea46f3be25d9abb1d0839c66246","tid":2059974,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T10:01:33.000Z","msg":"自從 Renee 接受訪問以來，其網站訂閱人數激增 5000多人，該網站於上周公開。<br />\n現在，她通過在成人訂閱網站 <a href=\"http://onlyfans.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fonlyfans.com&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjREzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=7df27cc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">onlyfans.com</a> 上出售自己的視頻和圖片，每月收入超過 90000 美元<br />\n<br />\n咁撚好賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e85160c6f23d106349b6bd64ae9ad8e304852d","tid":2059974,"uid":19437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T10:01:44.000Z","msg":"副偈好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac8f907e18384d39aff2b6a968b4c49c27da740","tid":2059974,"uid":266391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T10:04:43.000Z","msg":"邊渣車邊做愛？比人屌到反白眼架車就失去控制？"},{"pid":"b1be354b81f12b9fcc3a729b39207f4bb2f6f882","tid":2059974,"uid":70105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ac8f907e18384d39aff2b6a968b4c49c27da740","tid":2059974,"uid":266391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T10:04:43.000Z","msg":"邊渣車邊做愛？比人屌到反白眼架車就失去控制？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T10:08:42.000Z","msg":"如果行highway, 你架車係 tesla, 就唔會咁易炒。。。"},{"pid":"d1b5a1b2d6283aac9a27e3ff1afa00071b25be70","tid":2059974,"uid":75256,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79ba022a501830f9cb1b87e0ad33c8ff4d9a2057","tid":2059974,"uid":70105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T09:59:54.000Z","msg":"澳洲史上首位參賽 V8 Supercars 之 女車手 Renee Gracie ，突然宣佈決定退出賽車運動，轉而加入成人電影界，震驚當地賽車壇 